  "detailed_description": "Botanical Chronicle is the story of a lost robot looking for the last elements of life in nature that's been overwhelmed by technology.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/bc91d83263c3a32ab1d919d9b6ead828.poster.avif?t=1766422200\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/bc91d83263c3a32ab1d919d9b6ead828.webm?t=1766422200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/bc91d83263c3a32ab1d919d9b6ead828.mp4?t=1766422200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>take control of this robot in a third-person adventure over various gorgeous levels, fun obstacles, and breathtaking music. <br>Explore, unravel secrets paths, and escape dark forces of this mysterious landscape. Rivers, rocks, bushes seamlessly merging into digital realm and try to stop you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/da707fe08a4845f8edc466c01181abd7.poster.avif?t=1766422200\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/da707fe08a4845f8edc466c01181abd7.webm?t=1766422200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/da707fe08a4845f8edc466c01181abd7.mp4?t=1766422200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>See the world through the eyes of a robot and interact with the environment to find objectives. Be creative, fast, and sometimes as hidden as possible with the dangerous inhabitants of this mysterious world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/c4e4732544ec7e610a1d20b193ad38e6.poster.avif?t=1766422200\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/c4e4732544ec7e610a1d20b193ad38e6.webm?t=1766422200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/c4e4732544ec7e610a1d20b193ad38e6.mp4?t=1766422200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>All dark forces need a leader and here is one of the most stubborn and dangerous to stop you from saving the nature!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> For fans of all experimental story driven games.<br></li><li> Featuring gorgeous multiple soundtracks by acclaimed artists<br></li><li> A short game ( about an hour ) focused on a personal intimate story made by a solo developer</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/99e4146249092ec1771d975520c7fd45.poster.avif?t=1766422200\" width=592 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/99e4146249092ec1771d975520c7fd45.webm?t=1766422200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594970/extras/99e4146249092ec1771d975520c7fd45.mp4?t=1766422200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
